divs: Sighting DetailsI was laying on my back on my deck outside playing with my kids, noticed a stationary object in the sky, at first glance it looked round, when i got my camera and zoomed in looked like a boomerang i guess and it seemed like it was rotating slowly, i then lost site of it behind the clouds and it never returned
